<p>
  <span class="nym">Apollonius</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Ancient Greek</span> <i>Ἀπολλώνιος</i>, a derivative of <span class="lang">Ancient Greek</span> <i>Ἀπόλλων</i> 'Apollo', the god of light.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 2nd C saint. Wycliffite Bible (1395): <i>Apollos</i>. Geneva Bible (1560): <i>Apolló</i>.</p>
</div>
  
  


